prod_short_desc: Battle it out at the generator core!
prod_long_desc:
Play out exciting Jedi vs. Sith duels as Qui-Gon Jinn and Obi-Wan Kenobi go head-to-head against evil Darth Maul at the Naboo power generator. This detailed set features push-activated opening laser doors, a minifigure catapult function in the generator core and an opening purification chamber with removable ‘plasma’ element. Includes three minifigures.
Build the epic lightsaber battle scene against Darth Maul, including a minifigure catapult function
Featured in Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace
Includes Qui-Gon Jinn, Obi-Wan Kenobi and Darth Maul
LEGO Star Wars building toys are compatible with all LEGO construction sets for creative building
Measures over 5” high, 7” wide and 4” long
208 pieces – For boys and girls between the ages of 7 and 12 years old
